<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.bibleinterp.com/commentary/McKensie_020301.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.bibleinterp.com/commentary/McKensie_020301.htm" rel="nofollow">Steven McKenzie, Associate Professor Rhodes College, Memphis, Tennessee</a>.</li>
